snippet.textDisplay:
Jaffar Zaidi Hats off to your creative Genius. I have heard Javed Bashir and Akbar Ali sing Naina Morey before but this arrangement with Mann Atkhiya is just spell binding. it's not easy to redo something that Ustaad Bade Ghulam Ali Khan Sahab the Great performed and composed in his prime.  Amazing recreation, Masterful Job Loved it and i would have loved it even more if Amir Zaki played in the End too.. 

My Favorite of the Season after Yeh Faasle.

snippet.textDisplay: Take a bow Javed Bashir and Akbar Ali Sahab!!!!You people have made my day truly fantastic after hectic schedule at office. I have actually listened 2 songs, one is this and another is by Nescafe basement Season 4 'tum ek Gorakh Dhanda ho', a revisited version I would say. And I consider myself blessed by these two songs. Again take a bow Pakistani music industry. Indian music have been hijacked by some absolutely nonsense movies producers and directors and composers don't have guts to say this torture a strict "NO". They are just following Badshah, Honey Singh, Rafftar and God knows whom. History will be written that when Indian were corrupting music, Pakistanis were treasuring and gracing it.
